thread.title_full: Spa Store Australia reviewed by Dyanne

author: Dyanne
title: Dyanne
text: Only just discovered the Spa Store online. Needed to get new filters and had no-one local stock them. Ordered them (and a few extra things) online, and was pleasantly surprised at how easy and efficient everything was. Order arrived within a few days, and once again I have a wonderful, clean, just-like-new spa!
